data.description:
Mountain views and lots of trees near the creek! This home is nestled in the Verde Valley, a riparian area of Arizona with ample water, wineries, and outdoor activities. There is a lot of room to spread out in this house and workshop. Three bonus rooms could be an extra bedroom or multipurpose. 3-space RV garage includes a woodshop suitable for any craftsman. Brand new sinks, toilets, and carpeting. Every porch has a wonderful view of the hills surrounding the Verde Valley. Large half acre lot has mature peach and apple trees plus a raised bed area for planting your vegetable garden. Home is built on a solid concrete foundation. Quiet cul de sac lot. Home next door will also be for sale soon, perfect for a large family. Come take in the view and stake your claim near the creek! - Home to be sold "As Is"
- Base structure anchored in concrete block
- RV dump station on site
